----------------------------------Execution of Multiple Ardrones-----------------------------

Launch the tum_simulator for multiple drones by following instruction.
Copy the tum_simulator_multiple package in the src folder of tum_simulator_ws .
Open the terminal and write following commands.
$ cd tum_simulator_ws
$ catkin_make
$ source devel/setup.bash
$ roslaunch cvg_sim_gazebo testworld_with_three_ardrone.launch 

You will see 3 drones in the gazebo world.
Now go to catkin_ws and launch the file to fly the 3 drones on desired trajectory autonomously by following commands.
Open new terminal and execute following commands.
$ cd catkin_ws
$ source devel/setup.bash
$ rosrun ardrone_test up_and_away 

You will see 3 drones flying in gazebo.
